methods.name: public Builder setExcessPathLengthMeters(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float excessPathLengthMeters)
methods.comment:
* Sets the excess path length to be subtracted from pseudorange before using it in
         * calculating location.

methods.name: public Builder clearExcessPathLengthMeters()
methods.comment:
* Clears the excess path length. * *

This is to negate {@link #setExcessPathLengthMeters} call.

methods.name: public Builder setExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float excessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters)
methods.comment: Sets the error estimate (1-sigma) for the excess path length estimate

methods.name: public Builder clearExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters()
methods.comment:
* Clears the error estimate (1-sigma) for the excess path length estimate * *

This is to negate {@link #setExcessPathLengthUncertaintyMeters} call.

methods.name: public Builder setAttenuationDb(@FloatRange(from = 0.0f) float attenuationDb)
